%h3
  Teach on LearnTo
%p
  Teaching is a great way to meet new people with similar passions, become an expert in your field, and give back to your community. Fill out the following form and begin teaching soon!
%p
  If you're not sure what to teach, just think of something you love be it a sport, an instrument, or a technical skill!
%p
  Looking to teach a one time, scheduled lesson? Check out our #{link_to "scheduled lesson", new_event_path} form.
%hr.div-line
= form_for(@skill, {role: "form"}) do |f|
  .form-group
    = f.label :title, "Learn to..."
    %p.help-block
      Choose and interesting title to capture people's attention.
    = f.text_field :title, class: "form-control", placeholder: "i.e. 'Cook Italian food' or 'Build a website'"
  %hr.div-line
  .form-group
    = f.label :description
    %p.help-block
      Describe what you're going to help others learn.
    = f.text_area :description, rows: 5, class: "form-control", placeholder: "i.e. I can help you learn to make basic pastas, sauces, and pizzas! We can even work on making Italian deserts such as gelato!"
  %hr.div-line
  .form-group
    = f.label :qualifications
    %p.help-block
      Tell others why you're able to teach them.
    = f.text_area :qualifications, rows: 5, class: "form-control", placeholder: "i.e. I've been cooking for myself for many years and learned how to cook from my Italian mother. I absolutely love cooking (mainly because I like eating!) and would love to help someone pick it up."
  / %hr.div-line
  / .form-group
  /   = f.label :starts_at, "When? (Optional)"
  /   %p.help-block
  /     Only enter the date and time below if you have are scheduling this lesson for a specific time, otherwise people will be able to contact you to schedule a time and place to meet.
  /   = f.datetime_local_field :starts_at
  %hr.div-line
  .form-group
    = f.label :image
    %p.help-block
      Pick an image that describes your lesson.
    .upload-skill-picture.btn.btn-custom
      Upload an image that describes your skill
    %br
    = f.hidden_field :picture, class: "form-control"
  / %hr.div-line
  / .form-group
  /   = f.label :public
  /   = f.check_box :public
  /   %p.help-block
  /     Public lessons are visible to anyone.  Private lessons are visible to only those in your networks.
  %hr.div-line
    = f.submit "Submit", class: "btn btn-custom"